Hi yall,

My name's Hugo and I love css... Im a big fan of webdesign and I want progress in the mastering of some languages like html, css, javascript, jquery, php, sql and more...

One of my goal, is to create my websites by myself, front and back office included. But im not really an expert, I practise webdesign since only 3 years now
and i think i dont know the quarter of the quarter of the quarter of all those knowledges huhu.

My favorite part is the front-office part of the website. I know how to create a little backoffice but im not, like I said, a beast on this part.
That's why I work and cooperate with Julien, the french php monster(He knows more more than me about it and, however, he is just in highschool... A real monster, I told you!)

Since few months, my mind is focus on a big project. I love culture in general, videogames, cinema, books, animation etc. I wanted express my passion but I didnt know how.
And bam, this idea appeared: Create a website around this popular theme!

This project is open, you can check and browse inside. We hope you will enjoy it! We don't aim really great objectives for this website at the moment. It's a kind of birth,
we try to create a functionnal and optimized website in order to reuse it in the future, for our projects. 

Thanks for reading!

